replies.msg:
@charles_watts In terms of Partey, I certainly do know they have back up targets. Danilo Pereira is player that Arsenal have been interested in, there have been initial discussions with his representatives. Diawara at Roma is another player they have looked at as well. <br />
<br />
He is very much on the list of potential back up options. Arsenal went into this window with 5 possible options for the position. In terms of Houssem Aouar, I don't know of any back up targets if they can't get him.

